videos.description: Alabama RB Damien Harris has to be helped off the field after suffering an apparent injury against Kent State.
videos.headline: Alabama RB Harris helped off field

videos.description: Alabama QB Jalen Hurts breaks free for a 20-yard touchdown run to give Alabama a 7-0 lead over Kent State.
videos.headline: Alabama QB Hurts scampers for 20-yard TD

videos.description: Justin Rankin run for 47 yds to the Alab 28 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: J. Rankin run for 47 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Joshua Jacobs scores from one-yard out to give Alabama a 14-0 lead over Kent State.
videos.headline: Jacobs' TD run doubles Bama lead

videos.description: Alabama Tight End makes a great play after a a Jalen Hurts pass is tipped
videos.headline: Great Focus from O.J Howard to catch the ball for a First Down

videos.description: Alabama RB Joshua Jacobs fights his way through the Kent State defense to score from 24 yards out to give the Crimson Tide a 21-0 lead over Kent State.
videos.headline: Bama jump ahead 21-0 on 24-yard TD run

videos.description: Kavious Price run for a loss of 5 yards to the KntSt 24 Kavious Price fumbled, forced by Anthony Averett, recovered by Alab Ronnie Harrison
videos.headline: Kavious Price fumbles to give the ball back to Alabama

videos.description: Alabama QB Blake Barnett finds O.J. Howard for the 34-yard touchdown to put Alabama ahead of Kent State 34-0.
videos.headline: Bama takes 34-0 lead on 34-yard TD

videos.description: Alabama continues its dominant first half against Kent State with Xavian Marks returning a punt 75 yards to put the Crimson Tide ahead 41-0.
videos.headline: Xavian Marks returns punt 75 yards for Bama TD

videos.description: Alabama running back Damien Harris leaves in the first quarter and is replaced by Joshua Jacobs who rushes for 97 yards and two touchdowns as the Crimson Tide beat the Golden Flashes 48-0.
videos.headline: Harris leaves early in Alabama's rout of Kent State
